# The Vercel app is the JS serverless API (api/) + frontend (src/, dist/).
# The Python backends are deployed to Modal, not Vercel — excluding them keeps the
# CLI upload small (the repo's backend/ + finetuning/ are ~640M and otherwise blow
# past the upload limit, forcing git-only deploys).
backend
finetuning
.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
*.ipynb
